# Database Migrations

This folder contains SQL migration files for the Family Tree application.

## Setup (first time)
```bash
psql -U familytree_user -d familytree < database/001_initial_schema.sql
```

## Adding new migrations
- Name files sequentially: 002_add_photos.sql, 003_add_notes.sql etc.
- Always test locally before committing
- Never modify existing migration files — add new ones instead

## Restore from backup
```bash
dropdb familytree
createdb familytree
psql familytree < backups/backup-YYYY-MM-DD.sql
```